quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  6,82,"“(Palibe chikaiko kwa) amene adakhulupirira ndipo sadasakanize chikhulupiliro chawo ndi kupondereza (shirk), iwowo ali nacho chitetezo. Ndiponso iwo ndi omwe ali oongoka"
  6,83,"“Ndipo izi ndi zizindikiro Zathu (mitsutso Yathu), zomwe tidampatsa Ibrahim pa anthu ake. Timamtukulira ulemelero amene tamfuna. Ndithu Mbuye wako Ngwanzeru zakuya, Ngodziwa kwambiri"
  6,84,"“Ndipo tidampatsa (Ibrahim mwana wotchedwa) Ishaq ndi (mdzukulu wotchedwa) Ya’qub. Onse tidawaongola. Nayenso Nuh tidamuongola kale (asadadze Mneneri Ibrahim). Ndipo kuchokera m’mbumba yake (Nuh, tidamuongola) Daud, Sulaiman, Ayubu, Yûsuf, Mûsa, ndi Harun. Ndipo umo ndi momwe timawalipirira ochita zabwino"
  6,85,"“Tidamutsogoleranso Zakariya, Yahya, Isa (Yesu) ndi Iliyasa. Onse adali mwa anthu abwino"
  6,86,"“Ndi Ismail, Eliya, Yunus (Yona) ndi Luti (Loti). Onsewa tidawapatsa ubwino pa zolengedwa zonse"
  6,87,"“(Ndiponso tidawatsogolera) ena mwa atate awo, ana awo ndi abale awo. Ndipo tidawasankha ndi kuwaongolera ku njira yolunjika"
  6,88,“Ichi ndi chiongoko cha Allah. Ndi icho akuongolera yemwe wamfuna mwa akapolo Ake. Akadakhala kuti (aneneriwo) adamphatikiza (Allah ndi zina) zikadawaonongekera zimene ankachita
  6,89,"“Iwo ndi omwe tidawapatsa mabuku, chiweruzo, ndi uneneri. Choncho ngati awa (osakhulupirira) azikane izi, basi, tazipereka kale kwa anthu omwe sangazikane"
  6,90,"“Iwo ndi omwe Allah adawaongola choncho, tsatira chiongoko chawo. Nena: “Sindikukupemphani malipiro pa izi (zomwe ndikukuphunzitsanizi, koma ndikungotumikira Allah). Ichi sichina koma ndi ulaliki kwa zolengedwa (majini ndi anthu).”"